INSERT INTO `aanotion` VALUES (1,113,2669,'Atomic Symbols','en','en',3,'It is time to learn what the world is made of: the naturally occurring 98 elements and the remaining 20 heavier elements produced artificially'),(2,113,2669,'Atomic Numbers','en','en',3,'Also known as its proton number: the number of protons in the nucleus of an atom, identical to the charge of the nucleus, represented by the symbol Z'),(3,113,7443,'European Capitals','en','en',4,'Take a few minutes to learn the names and locations of the most important european cities. Learn to identify them and place them in a map '),(4,113,2671,'African Capitals','en','en',4,'See how easy it is to learn the name and location of the capital cities of all the countries in Africa, from Angola to Zimbabwe'),(5,113,7440,'Oceania Capitals','en','en',4,'Start to learn the capitals of the world with the shortest set: Oceania\'s 14 sovereignties in the South Pacific'),(6,113,7442,'Asian Capitals','en','en',4,'Take the challenge and learn the capital cities of the world\'s most populated and most diverse continent.'),(7,113,2672,'Americas Capitals','en','en',4,'How many of the Latin American countries do you recognize? Can you place them in a map?'),(8,113,51,'Spanish Verbs 4','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about to keep pace with popular culture, and a fast growing percentage of native speakers: 50M by 2015 in the U.S. alone'),(9,113,51,'Spanish Verbs 5','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because 350M people in the world speak it as a mother tongue? This sector of the western world is also growing fast'),(10,113,51,'Spanish Verbs 2','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because other Romance languages like Italian, Portuguese, and French become easier to read, understand and speak'),(11,113,51,'Spanish Verbs 3','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because the limits of your language are the limits of your universe -Ludwig Wittgenstein'),(14,113,7396,'Multiplication Challenge I','en','en',2,'How fast can you multiply ? Here you can practice simple multiplication tables type problems involving the positive natural numbers from 2 up to 12'),(15,113,51,'Spanish Verbs 1','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish? How about to be able to read Cervante\'s Don Quijote or Garcia Márquez\'s Cien años de soledad in the original text'),(16,113,51,'Essential Spanish','en','es',1,'Travelling to a Spanish speaking country ? Need to learn Spanish in a hurry? Here is a list of the essential words and phrases to get by'),(17,113,53,'Essential French','en','fr',1,'Travelling to a French speaking country ? Need to learn French in a hurry? Here is a list of the essential words and phrases to get by'),(19,113,2716,'Famous People','en','en',5,'Famous and infamous personalities who figured throughout history and around the world as well known and remain so until today'),(20,113,2717,'Geologic Scale','en','en',5,'The time keeping system used to describe the timing of events that have occurred throughout Earth’s history from it\'s birth until today'),(21,113,2715,'Greek Mythology','en','en',20,'Many great works of literature refer back to Greek mythology, and there is no way to understand them without knowing the basics of this topic'),(23,113,7396,'Multiplication Challenge II','en','en',2,'Can you multiply beyond 10 ? Here you can practice simple multiplication tables type problems involving the numbers from 12 up to 19'),(24,113,51,'Spanish Nouns 1','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because it is easy! It requires no new alphabet and written Spanish is entirely phonetic (i.e. read as written)'),(25,113,51,'Spanish Nouns 2','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because the U.S. is on its way to become the world\'s largest Spanish speaking country by 2060 with ca. 130M'),(26,113,51,'Spanish Nouns 3','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about to unlock travel destinations. There are about 350M Spanish speakers in the world inhabiting some of the coolest places'),(27,113,51,'Spanish Nouns 4','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about to enjoy world class films by star directors Almodóvar, Cuarón, and Del Toro in the original script'),(28,113,51,'Spanish Nouns 5','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How baout to improve your employment potential. Many jobs become available to those who speak a second language.'),(29,113,51,'Spanish Words 1','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because people who speak Spanish often have opportunities to work in trade or business fields'),(30,113,51,'Spanish Words 2','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about to improve your knowledge of English. Spanish is a Romance language and English too has many words of Latin origin'),(31,113,51,'Spanish Words 3','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about because words of Latin origin are especially helpful in certain professions like science, medicine, law, etc'),(32,113,51,'Spanish Words 4','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about becuase it\'s the fourth most commonly spoken language in the world (after English, Chinese and Hindustani)'),(33,113,51,'Spanish Words 5','en','es',1,'Why learn Spanish ? How about becuase Spanish is one of the easiest foreign languages to learn. Much of its vocabulary is similar to English'),(34,113,53,'French Nouns 1','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because for English speakers, French is the easiest language to learn. English is the stepchild of German and French'),(35,113,53,'French Nouns 2','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because words of Latin origin are especially helpful in certain professions like science, medicine, law, etc'),(36,113,53,'French Nouns 3','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about to improve your knowledge of English. French is a Romance language and English too has many words of Latin origin'),(37,113,53,'French Nouns 4','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about to improve your employment potential. Many jobs become available to those who speak a second language'),(38,113,53,'French Nouns 5','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about to enjoy world class films by star directors Godard, Truffaut and Tati in the original script'),(39,113,53,'French Verbs 5','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about to unlock some beautiful travel destinations from Canada to exotic places in Africa'),(40,113,53,'French Verbs 4','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because 140M people in the world speak it as a mother tongue? 220M speak it as a first and second language'),(41,113,53,'French Verbs 3','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because other Romance languages like Italian, Portuguese, and Spanish become easier to read, understand and speak'),(42,113,53,'French Verbs 2','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because the limits of your language are the limits of your universe -Ludwig Wittgenstein'),(43,113,53,'French Verbs 1','en','fr',1,'Why learn French? How about to be able to read Duma\'s Count of Monte Cristo or Victor Hugo\'s Les Misérables  in the original text'),(44,113,53,'French Words 1','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because French is the language of love. You can practically insult someone in French while still sounding polite'),(45,113,53,'French Words 2','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because it is an official language in 29 countries ( La Francophonie). It is also an official language of all UN agencies'),(46,113,53,'French Words 3','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because all over Europe, French is still the main second language taught in school'),(47,113,53,'French Words 4','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because half of Africa speaks French, and both Russia and China based their revolutions on the french model'),(48,113,53,'French Words 5','en','fr',1,'Why learn French ? How about because it is an official language of the UN, the European Union, UNESCO, NATO, and the International Olympic Committee.'),(49,113,52,'German Nouns 1','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German is the most widely spoken language in Europe with 120M native speakers'),(50,113,52,'German Nouns 2','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because it is also an official language of Austria, Switzerland, Luxembourg, and Liechtenstein'),(51,113,52,'German Nouns 3','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because it is the native language of parts of Italy, Belgium, the Netherlands, Denmark, France, and Poland'),(52,113,52,'German Nouns 4','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How abut because Germany has the 3rd strongest economy and is the #1 export nation in the world'),(53,113,52,'German Nouns 5','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German is the second most spoken language after Russian in Eastern Europe'),(54,113,52,'German Verbs 5','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German companies account for 1M jobs in the United States, giving German speaking job candidates an advantage'),(55,113,52,'German Verbs 4','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German-speaking tourists travel wide and far, and are the world’s biggest spenders when on holiday.'),(56,113,52,'German Verbs 3','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German is the second most commonly used scientific language in the world'),(57,113,52,'German Verbs 2','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because German is the language of Goethe, Kafka, Mozart, Bach and Beethoven. '),(58,113,52,'German Verbs 1','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because of its rich world class literature: Goethe, the Brothers Grimm, Hermann Hesse, Schiller, Mann'),(59,113,52,'German Words 1','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because of the many works in mathematics and science originally in German by Leibnitz, Einstein, Planck, Gauss, Hilbert'),(60,113,52,'German Words 2','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? How about because of the many contributions in Philosophy originally in German by Kant, Hegel, Schoppenhauer, Nietzsche'),(61,113,52,'German Words 3','en','de',1,'Why learn German ? 